'''Electronic Freightways''' was a mysterious cargo corporation. The company was shrouded in mystery, as there was no real known information behind the corporation. Curiously, it would only hire independent [[Pilot/Legends|pilots]] to carry the cargo across [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]].

